content: Just got off a call with a potential investor. They're interested in our project but want to see a demo with live trading data. It’s a big ask, but we're ready to show what we've got.
The city skyline from my window reminds me of the endless possibilities. We're integrating market sentiment analysis now, and the model’s accuracy is climbing again. Slow progress is still progress.
Our smart contract executed its first trade based on AI predictions. It was a small win, but a win nonetheless. Every trade is a learning opportunity, and we're documenting everything.

Just got the latest feedback from our investor. They're impressed, but want us to focus on scalability. It's time to think bigger, not just about the model but how it fits into the larger DeFi ecosystem.
